{"word":"Sarah or Sarai","slug":"sarah-or-sarai","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Sarah or Sarai</b> - wife of Abraham<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=11&verse=29'>Gen 11:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=16&verse=5'>Gen 16:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=17&verse=15'>Gen 17:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=18&verse=12'>Gen 18:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=20&verse=2'>Gen 20:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=21&verse=6'>Gen 21:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=23&verse=1'>Gen 23:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=9&verse=9'>Rom 9:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=11&verse=11'>Heb 11:11</a><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=60&chapter=3&verse=6'>1Pe 3:6</a><p/>--\"The Mother of Nations\"<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=17&verse=15'>Gen 17:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=17&verse=16'>Gen 17:16</a><p/>Beautiful<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=12&verse=11'>Ge 12:11</a><p/>Impatient of divine delays, attempts to anticipate the plans of<p/>providence, Compare Gen 15:4 with Gen 16:2<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=15&verse=4'>Gen 15:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=16&verse=2'>Gen 16:2</a><p/>Brings family trouble upon herself<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=16&verse=5'>Gen 16:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=16&verse=6'>Gen 16:6</a><p/>Again disbelieves God's promise<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=18&verse=12'>Ge 18:12-15</a><p/>The ruling personality in the home<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=21&verse=10'>Ge 21:10-12</a><p/>In spite of her infirmities honoured of God<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=17&verse=15'>Ge 17:15</a><p/>Mentioned in the roll of Bible worthies<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=11&verse=11'>Heb 11:11</a><p/><b>--SEE</b> Notable Women, WOMEN"}]}